  "detailed_description": "In Task Force 9, victory lies in mastering the art of stealth and employing strategic tricks. Relying solely on shooting won't cut it for most people. Set ambushes, distract guards, gather intel, take human shields, and work as a team to overcome challenges. Embrace the game's complexity, and success will be yours to conquer. Adapt, strategize, and outsmart your foes!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/57549e1eb0ef11416beaaa8a28896c07.poster.avif?t=1736599223\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/57549e1eb0ef11416beaaa8a28896c07.webm?t=1736599223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/57549e1eb0ef11416beaaa8a28896c07.mp4?t=1736599223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game has:<br>2 camping 3 levels each and procedural building to practice.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/22ce7749c404663eaa5888a8b5bb4c16.poster.avif?t=1736599223\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/22ce7749c404663eaa5888a8b5bb4c16.webm?t=1736599223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/22ce7749c404663eaa5888a8b5bb4c16.mp4?t=1736599223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Extra arrest level where you need to take out the guards before you take the target out (more are planned):<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/e0e5523d8710df79bc0e9486425f6c1d.poster.avif?t=1736599223\" width=720 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/e0e5523d8710df79bc0e9486425f6c1d.webm?t=1736599223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/e0e5523d8710df79bc0e9486425f6c1d.mp4?t=1736599223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br>This pre-release version welcomes your valuable feedback to improve and balance the game. <br><br>Our Discord server is also available for feedback and support: <br>You can also find more information and hidden tips on YouTube: <br><br>Thank you support and we hope you will enjoy the game!",
  "about_the_game": "In Task Force 9, victory lies in mastering the art of stealth and employing strategic tricks. Relying solely on shooting won't cut it for most people. Set ambushes, distract guards, gather intel, take human shields, and work as a team to overcome challenges. Embrace the game's complexity, and success will be yours to conquer. Adapt, strategize, and outsmart your foes!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/57549e1eb0ef11416beaaa8a28896c07.poster.avif?t=1736599223\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/57549e1eb0ef11416beaaa8a28896c07.webm?t=1736599223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/57549e1eb0ef11416beaaa8a28896c07.mp4?t=1736599223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game has:<br>2 camping 3 levels each and procedural building to practice.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/22ce7749c404663eaa5888a8b5bb4c16.poster.avif?t=1736599223\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/22ce7749c404663eaa5888a8b5bb4c16.webm?t=1736599223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/22ce7749c404663eaa5888a8b5bb4c16.mp4?t=1736599223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Extra arrest level where you need to take out the guards before you take the target out (more are planned):<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/e0e5523d8710df79bc0e9486425f6c1d.poster.avif?t=1736599223\" width=720 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/e0e5523d8710df79bc0e9486425f6c1d.webm?t=1736599223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414680/extras/e0e5523d8710df79bc0e9486425f6c1d.mp4?t=1736599223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br>This pre-release version welcomes your valuable feedback to improve and balance the game. <br><br>Our Discord server is also available for feedback and support: <br>You can also find more information and hidden tips on YouTube: <br><br>Thank you support and we hope you will enjoy the game!",
